txt.en: 'Ah good work, the hens are all safe within their cage. And you made sure to lock it properly?'
Cangoras is at the Palace of Eldacar.\n\nYou should speak to Cangoras.
The Chicken coop is located outside the Palace of Eldacar.\n\nYou should bring the Chickens to the Chicken coop.
Bring the Chickens to the Chicken coop
Hens providing eggs and meat for the troops in Osgiliath have escaped their confines and should be found and returned before the enemy finds out.
The Chickens have been returned to their coop
Escaped Chickens can be found roaming around Western Osgiliath.\n\nYou should find the escaped chickens.

'The hens have escaped! We've been keeping hens near the Western wall to provide eggs and meat for our soldiers. Someone didn't latch the cage door properly last night and now all the hens are missing!\n\n'You must find them quickly before those nasty Orcs find out and pluck them up for themselevs!'
